original: The denim specialists! Tanktop believes that they can charge four times as much for their jeans because they use colored stitching. We disagree! Our Tanktop replicas are made of denim-effect canvas and cost just $20!! They won't weigh you down in the rain!
translated: 牛仔布专家！Tanktop相信他们的裤子比普通裤子贵三倍，因为他们用了彩色缝线。我们不同意！我们的Tanktop高仿裤采用帆布制作，节省了牛仔布，还只要$20！！帆布不会在雨天拖垮你！
